{"title_page": "Park Bottom", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=February 2016}}\n{{Use British English|date=February 2016}}\n{{Infobox UK place\n|static_image= Park Bottom - geograph.org.uk - 97801.jpg\n|static_image_width= 250px\n|static_image_caption= Park Bottom\n|country= England\n|region= South West England\n|map_type=Cornwall\n|official_name=Park Bottom\n|cornish_name= \n|civil_parish=  [[Illogan]]\n|unitary_england=     [[Cornwall Council|Cornwall]]\n|lieutenancy_england =[[Cornwall]]\n|os_grid_reference= SW669425\n|coordinates = {{coord|50.236|-5.270|display=inline,title}}\n|population =\n|population_ref = \n|post_town=        \n|postcode_area=   \n|postcode_district= \n|dial_code= \n|\n|hide_services=yes  \n}}\n'''Park Bottom''' is a hamlet north of [[Pool, Cornwall|Pool]] and near [[Illogan]] in west [[Cornwall]], England.<ref name=OS203>{{cite map|title=Ordnance Survey: Landranger map sheet 203 ''Land's End & Isles of Scilly (St Ives & Lizard Point)''|ISBN=978-0-319-23289-7|publisher=Ordnance Survey|date=2009}}</ref><ref>Ordnance Survey ''One-inch Map of Great Britain; Land's End, sheet 189''. 1961</ref>\nThe village centers around one junction in the lower part of the town. This 5-way junction has roads leading to[[Camborne| ]],[[Illogan| ]],[[Portreath| ]] and Pool.\nThe village has three commercial buildings in the centre, a Premier convenience store, a pub called The New Inn and a hair salon.\n\n==References==\n{{Portal|Cornwall}}\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Cornwall|state=collapsed}}\n\n[[Category:Hamlets in Cornwall]]\n\n\n{{Cornwall-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=February 2016}}\n{{Use British English|date=February 2016}}\n{{Infobox UK place\n|static_image= Park Bottom - geograph.org.uk - 97801.jpg\n|static_image_width= 250px\n|static_image_caption= Park Bottom\n|country= England\n|region= South West England\n|map_type=Cornwall\n|official_name=Park Bottom\n|cornish_name= \n|civil_parish=  [[Illogan]]\n|unitary_england=     [[Cornwall Council|Cornwall]]\n|lieutenancy_england =[[Cornwall]]\n|os_grid_reference= SW669425\n|coordinates = {{coord|50.236|-5.270|display=inline,title}}\n|population =\n|population_ref = \n|post_town=        \n|postcode_area=   \n|postcode_district= \n|dial_code= \n|\n|hide_services=yes  \n}}\n'''Park Bottom''' is a hamlet north of [[Pool, Cornwall|Pool]] and near [[Illogan]] in west [[Cornwall]], England.<ref name=OS203>{{cite map|title=Ordnance Survey: Landranger map sheet 203 ''Land's End & Isles of Scilly (St Ives & Lizard Point)''|ISBN=978-0-319-23289-7|publisher=Ordnance Survey|date=2009}}</ref><ref>Ordnance Survey ''One-inch Map of Great Britain; Land's End, sheet 189''. 1961</ref>\nThe village centers around one junction in the lower part of the town. This 5-way junction has roads leading to[[Camborne| ]],[[Illogan| ]],[[Portreath| ]] and Pool.\nThe village has three commercial buildings in the centre, a Premier convenience store, a pub called The New Inn and a hair salon.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Cornwall|state=collapsed}}\n\n[[Category:Hamlets in Cornwall]]\n\n\n{{Cornwall-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Gazamp", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eReferences:AddedPortal:Cornwall", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Park_Bottom"}
